      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY CUPCAKE (1) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from nine starts. Hit the frame latest (23.15) when second at this track in a NG. Rates on top and should go close. JASPER DARKE (2) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (30.28) there two back. Solid record here at this trip including 15 wins. Cannot be taken lightly. BELTONE BOY (4) goes very well this course and distance starting 17 times for six wins and six minors. Was out of the placings last time (22.61) at Gosford in a NG, finishing fourth and beaten 4.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. BARRAMUNDI LOU (7) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when third (23.17) in a NG over 400m at this track.",
